    "Results and Discussion DatasetsThis study involved the assessment of our approach using two publicly available BUS image datasets.",
    "Dataset 1 (BUSI) was provided online by Al-Dhabyani et al. [21] and contains 600 BUS images of female patients in a total of 780 PNG format images and their corresponding masks with an average image size of 500px × 500px.",
    "The 780 images were split into three classes: normal, benign, and malignant.",
    "The benign class had 487 breast tumors, and the malignant class had 210 images.",
    "In our work, we only used the malignant and benign."
  ],
